     <h3>Vidya Lakshmi portal for educational loan scheme</h3>
     <h5>Department of Higher Education</h5>
     <p>Lakshmi Portal provides a single window for students to access information and make application for Educational Loans provided by Banks. Students can view, apply and track the education loan applications to banks anytime, anywhere by accessing the portal. The portal also provides linkages to National Scholarship Portal. This portal has been developed under the guidance of Department of Financial Services, Department of Higher Education and Indian Banks Association.</p>
     </div>
