    <div class="row" id="row2">
    <h4>Benifits :</h4>
    <p>We will ensure that no student misses out on higher education for lack of funds. The IT based mechanism under the Pradhan Mantri Vidya Lakshmi Karyakram is expected to provide to students a single window electronic platform for Scholarships and Educational Loans.With a view to enable all poor and middle class students to pursue higher education of their choice without any constraint of funds.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="row" id="row2">
    <h4>Application Procedure :</h4>
    <ul>
     <li>The first step is to register on the Vidyalakshmi login portal by Creating your login ID and password.</li>
     <li>Fill up the Common Education Loan Application Form (CELAF) by providing all the necessary details.</li>
     <li>While filling out your details on the vidyalakshmi loan application portal, make sure to save your details at every step.</li>
     <li>After filling the form, the applicant can search for Educational Loan and APPLY as per his/her needs, eligibility and convenience.</li> 
     <li>Alternatively, the applicant can also search for Educational Loan after login and apply for the suitable Educational Loan by filling the CELAF.</li>

   </ul>  
    
    </div>
