    <ul>
     <li>KYC document</li>
     <li>Residence Proof</li>
     <li>Last qualification marksheet,Score card of degree or diploma</li>
     <li>Latest admission proof</li>
     <li>Basic qualifiaction reord such as HSC and SCC</li>
     <li>Bank statement</li>
     <li>Income Tax document</li>
     <li>Documents of ownership of asset</li>
     <li>Guarantee form</li>
     
   </ul>  
    
